Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:26.88,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(498,0)}Can't focus. My body is still puzzled about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.63,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'm trembling. I can't stop even if I try to control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:34.38,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Although neither sun nor moon are on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:35.80,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}"I've no choice but to try,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:38.47,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Those were the words I muttered to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:44.06,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}The odds aren't on my side, but running way'd be gutless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.06,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}Even if I can't see the future, I'll just have to win it over with courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:51.57,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Need to keep distance from the target as I hold myself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.86,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(298,0)}All that's needed for victory is pride to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:57.95,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Will we celebrate with the wine of victory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:01.95,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Or'll we end up kissing their feet in defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:05.71,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}There are two outcomes to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:09.42,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}I want to control destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.76,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I need to seize the golden opportunity with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.84,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll finish it up with my best poker face,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:23.77,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,458)}And drag them into a world of illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:30.15,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I'll find my way out of this endless pressure game,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.15,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}And leap over the borderline of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:38.86,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}How many? What'll I need to sacrifice to make it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:43.12,OP03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,500)}What is the one thing I don't want to let go?
