Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:59.85,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}I stand in the city, staring off into space with lonely eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:05.19,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't find warmth on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:10.70,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)}By meeting you, I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:16.54,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}How much strength love could give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:21.79,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Even if we part and meet again, I want to meet at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:27.09,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Then we'll hold hands to ensure we'll never be separated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:32.30,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't sleep by myself, 'cause I can't dream without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:38.06,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}So take me to a place where uncertainty can't reach us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:43.31,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}And let us bring light to the night sky with no stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:45.82,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}So long as you're with me, I can go to world's end.{\i0}
