Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:54.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:02:00.89,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,To look at it in a positive light, it means I have the chance to assassinate him in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:09.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do me a favor and let the Colonel know that Scar is still lurking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.40,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.07,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:22.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for telling me about Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... So that's how things were in Ishbal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:45.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She was willing to tell me everything, despite me being a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:49.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemists are people who pursue the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:50.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...we didn't even know about things so close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So the Colonel is looking at the future that'll take place after he accomplishes his goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The future that'll take place after he accomplishes his goal, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:06.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, what do you plan to do after you get your body back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I want to taste Winry's apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.63,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:23.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really thought about it, since I've always been so intent on getting my limbs back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:30.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll start off by going around to Granny and Master and letting them know first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they've really done a lot for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.65,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all greet us with smiles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to see their smiles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a tight spot, but that sort of cheered me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something good to tell you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't use alchemy at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And it turns out others couldn't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about that girl and Scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. They were the only ones who could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:14.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's something different about their alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Something we're not aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're not at a dead end yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That midget left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.62,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say where she was headed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.91,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,All of Central? Without a single lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We do have a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.93,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.22,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,A gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.43,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.94,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,...couldn't you have brought me magazines with a lot of cute girls in 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.69,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be slacking off while we're gone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.69,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,You're heading off already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:04.90,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.57,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to taste some western specialty dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.45,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better take care of this place while we're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.04,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.00,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.55,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you eat a lot and grow bigger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.26,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Protect everyone while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.72,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Fuery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.55,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.47,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Falman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.22,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't left yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.02,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,I came to return something to the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.52,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,It sure was a short stay in Central...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.15,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Were you transferred to Southern Headquarters, Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.57,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Opposite from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.58,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's cold over in Northern Headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.08,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, so long, Sergeant Fuery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.33,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell. May we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.76,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.22,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pick up something I left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.18,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Scar is still lurking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.98,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have to be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.36,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Since I no longer have a skilled bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.32,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.37,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to put you through so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.04,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I chose the wrong person to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.00,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,"If I ever stray away from my path, shoot me right away."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That was the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.59,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions are still within the permissible range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.80,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.60,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't slack off, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,My pawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.00,Default,Fuery,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my hobbies got the best of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,My bishop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.17,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! It is an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.29,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,My rook...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.67,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.21,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,My knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.88,Default,Havoc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stupid, so I had a rough time at the military academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.01,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish, I'll follow you to the depths of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.43,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...even my queen was taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's too early...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.11,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...for checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like this! This is what the cat looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a little girl carrying this thing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:03.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, please ignore that alien he's holding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows anything about that black and white cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she left Central already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Eastern Alchemy from Xing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask around about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:33.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I didn't really want to ask you for any favors...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Speaking of being in debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,...give me my money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So you remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How much do I owe you again? 500 cenz?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,520 Cenz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to play it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell! You're so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll never make it big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm going to hold on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it when you become the Führer President.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hawkeye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She told me about Ishbal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.75,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep the change for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll be getting it back for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes, I'll borrow money from you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,With the promise "I'll give this back to you when you turn this country into a democracy".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And when you get that back, I'll borrow from you again and make you agree to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.94,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I have a long life ahead of me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Quit worrying the Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.25,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,You sure took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.29,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be waiting here until I went bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.26,Default,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.68,Default,Van,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You look well, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.77,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.36,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Madam Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.73,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.11,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Not very well at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to liven up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:39.90,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,What can I start you out with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually recovering right now, so alcohol is a no-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be asking for the specialty, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.71,Default,Madam,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:59.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant General Grumman, you have a call from Central from a lady by the name of Madam Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.80,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:05.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Please don't tell civilians about our secret line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.48,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,It just means that I'm not completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.06,Default,Grum,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has a task for this old geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:26.58,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your arm, failed to protect the young master,\Nand are now reduced to such a state...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.33,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.75,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.92,Default-alt,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,You still call yourself a chosen member of the Yao Clan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.80,Default-alt,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Have some honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.92,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,She's injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.05,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.89,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really lose it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.68,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really lose your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.73,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.44,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.94,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.03,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:15.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,As we promised, we'll set you up with an automail mechanic right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.09,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.05,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.17,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't ask you to help us any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.09,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll somehow find an automail mechanic on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just leave you like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:34.98,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the enemy knows what Lan Fan looks like, we can't take any actions that may involve your friend in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.16,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my granddaughter's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.62,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.46,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't a doctor that should be receiving gratitude-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.83,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Nox, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.01,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.84,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not kind enough to let you weirdos stay forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.01,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.65,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Emperor's condition is worsening by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:23.61,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,We must get the young master back and return to our country with the stone as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.32,Default,Fu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:26.57,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.50,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, you fiends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.88,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,We shall be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.95,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget my gratitude to you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.79,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Nox, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:18.96,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}now{\i0\fscx30} {\r} I'm starting to act like a doctor after all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.34,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.38,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:27.72,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.80,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.26,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.72,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:35.97,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.77,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,We had some business around here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.94,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.94,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you've lost some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.53,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.28,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,Is your work keeping you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.70,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've been performing on corpses as always-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.45,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:59.08,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,I treated two live patients this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.50,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.79,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Me, saving people's lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.01,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, I'm studying to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:13.01,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you've been going through a rough time ever since you returned from Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.10,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you didn't quit your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:21.60,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Dad! As the doctor you are and have always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.48,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.07,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.45,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,The coffee's not too tasty, but have a cup or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.16,Default,Son,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's such a mess in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:43.54,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let's get this place cleaned up while Dad makes us coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:50.47,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,God, if you really do exist, please overlook this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:58.39,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me can enjoy a cup of coffee with his family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:13.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And with this, Ishbal has completely fallen under the control of the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:16.37,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Major Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.58,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like the philosopher's stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:25.21,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to perform transmutations beyond my dreams while ignoring the concept of equivalent exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Make a record of the details and submit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.63,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Now give us the stone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.93,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done, Kimblee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:41.22,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's only you all who know where the stone is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.68,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.77,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.53,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:04.96,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Kimblee. You're being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.76,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.43,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an order from the higher-ups?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why weren't you put on\Ndeath row after killing five officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What trick did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.48,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.94,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because of my natural virtues?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh, you bomberman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:39.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are the higher-ups thinking, releasing a freak like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:51.63,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jailer, thanks for taking care of me for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.68,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Just a token of my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:04.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please, take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.86,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boring old toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.41,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it to your kid or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.54,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.38,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.43,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.60,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your release.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.14,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you all who let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:49.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.69,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We've run into a labor shortage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:55.36,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, you have a job for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.49,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to remember Doctor Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.66,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,The scientist who helped create the philosopher's stone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.12,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I remember him very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.66,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He may...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.33,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,"May have"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.96,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's still not clear yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.34,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,One of the chimeras we placed as a watchdog was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Marcoh is an alchemist especially skilled in organic transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.26,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse may have been a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.18,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,And to make matters worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.73,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,there's a possibility he's on the run with Scar, an Ishbalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.19,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So, how does that sound to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:37.32,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,...as someone who was ordered to annihilate Ishbal, the Crimson Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.28,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.57,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,If it's an Ishbalan that I forgot to kill, then it's hard to let this one pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.16,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're allowed to kill Scar on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.75,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But bring Marcoh back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:54.13,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You released me from jail for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:20:00.88,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Once we capture Marcoh, we're going to wipe a town off the map just to show him who he's messing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.18,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a pleasant job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.43,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a nasty person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.56,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally use this, after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:15.86,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,That may not be enough if we're\Nplanning to destroy an entire town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.86,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.45,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make this out of Ishbalans, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.91,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,It's made out of the guys who were researching the stone under Doctor Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.16,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.00,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help me escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.55,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.88,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There are still things I need to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.80,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,About the alchemist named Kimblee, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:53.31,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,...there were parts I couldn't understand in the research documents my brother left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.10,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Research documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:00.52,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,"There's something strange about this country's alchemy" are the words he left me before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.61,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Something about that should be written in the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.78,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're a skilled alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.53,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to comprehend it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:11.87,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Something strange about this country's alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:16.08,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Master. The little girl came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.50,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Scar! You were okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.13,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We have another friend with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.76,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.26,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:30.35,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He's a man who created a philosopher's stone and assisted in the Ishbalan Extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.31,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone! For immortality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:37.56,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Marcoh, do you know how to make the stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.44,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,How?! Please, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.53,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:43.73,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.82,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't wish for such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.63,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I only destroyed the exterior of his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.34,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop his bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:07.55,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:12.18,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to destroy his face so others won't be able to tell who he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.18,Default-alt,May,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mister Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:14.10,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:16.06,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:20.52,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,To the place I hid the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:23.61,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,North.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:03.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The figure hidden all this time reveals himself with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:08.63,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx96}With that, a new threat endangers the tangled web Central is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:14.30,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:18.72,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 32, The Führer's Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:23.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be better to not know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.39,0:24:24.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps...
